# Motion_Correction
This repository contains code to perform motion correction for two-photon image data. This code is integrated into a GUI to allow for easy batch analysis, and provides options to use two different algorithms to perform motion correction; 1) Suite2p alogrithm, 2) Patchwarp. Both algorithms provide options to perform rigid and non-rigid motion correction. The scripts in this repository borrows heavily from Suite2p.
